source.name: NIST belltestdata (Shalm et al. 2015; time-tag repository)

schema.alice_click_t: uint64 timetag counts (aligned to Alice PPS=0)
schema.alice_click_delay: uint64 timetag counts since last sync
schema.bob_click_delay: uint64 timetag counts since last sync
schema.offset_counts: int64 counts added to Bob times to align PPS

notes: normalized_events.npz is a compressed export of the time-tag clicks for max_seconds.
Trial-based denominators are computed from the published hdf5 build.
